reviewText: Arrived on time and excellent condition. Have two of the  titles already but sometimes I want to watch all three together I know lazy but true. But it is a good set of picks to have so don't have to buy all three and can enjoy at your leisure. I would definitely recommend this set of movies.
Title: 3 Disaster Movies: Weather Wars / Scorcher / Miami Magma

reviewText: If you like disaster movies, and I do, this will be one you can watch without trying to figure out the science of it.  Kinda lame but, still good entertainment.  I don't watch this kind of movie to learn anything, anyway.
